Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:48.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}波に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:58.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}さらわれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:15.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}そっと　そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:26.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}消えてもかまわないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:36.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}まだ　残る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:42.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}気持ちはどこかへ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:53.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}あ　いろを落とすでしょう
