Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:23:02.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}日が射すまでに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:18.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}そっと　そっと
